{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"ideedf7090-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1638b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1638b"},"text":"§ 1638b.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Enforcement","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ideedf7091-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1638b/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Warnings","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"If the Secretary determines that a retailer or person engaged in the business of supplying a covered commodity to a retailer is in violation of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1638a"},"text":"section 1638a of this title","children":[],"tail":", the Secretary shall—"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ideedf7092-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1638b/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" notify the retailer ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002190"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002190"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" So in original. Probably should be “retailer or person”."}],"tail":" of the determination of the Secretary; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ideedf7093-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1638b/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" provide the retailer ","children":[{"tag":"sup","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" a 30-day period, beginning on the date on which the retailer "},{"tag":"sup","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" receives the notice under paragraph (1) from the Secretary, during which the retailer "},{"tag":"sup","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" may take necessary steps to comply with "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1638a"},"text":"section 1638a of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"ideedf7094-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1638b/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Fines","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"If, on completion of the 30-day period described in subsection (a)(2), the Secretary determines that the retailer or person engaged in the business of supplying a covered commodity to a retailer has—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ideedf7095-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1638b/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" not made a good faith effort to comply with ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1638a"},"text":"section 1638a of this title","children":[],"tail":", and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"ideedf7096-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9","identifier":"/us/usc/t7/s1638b/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" continues to willfully violate ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1638a"},"text":"section 1638a of this title","children":[],"tail":" with respect to the violation about which the retailer or person received notification under subsection (a)(1),"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"after providing notice and an opportunity for a hearing before the Secretary with respect to the violation, the Secretary may fine the retailer or person in an amount of not more than $1,000 for each violation.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"ideedf7097-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1946-08-14/ch966"},"text":"Aug. 14, 1946, ch. 966","children":[],"tail":", title II, § 283, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/171/tX/s10816"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–171, title X, § 10816","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-05-13"},"text":"May 13, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/116/535"},"text":"116 Stat. 535","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234/tXI/s11002/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234, title XI, § 11002(3)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-05-22"},"text":"May 22, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/1354"},"text":"122 Stat. 1354","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s4/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246, § 4(a)","children":[],"tail":", title XI, § 11002(3), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-06-18"},"text":"June 18, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/1664"},"text":"122 Stat. 1664","children":[],"tail":", 2116.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"ideedf7098-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"ideedf7099-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"ideedf709a-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234","children":[],"tail":" and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":" made identical amendments to this section. The amendments by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234","children":[],"tail":" were repealed by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s4/a"},"text":"section 4(a) of Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"ideedf709b-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2008—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s11002/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246, § 11002(3)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated subsec. (b) as (a) and substituted “retailer or person engaged in the business of supplying a covered commodity to a retailer” for “retailer” in introductory provisions, added subsec. (b), and struck out former subsecs. (a) and (c) which related to applicability of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1636b"},"text":"section 1636b of this title","children":[],"tail":" to a violation of this subchapter and fine for violation of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s1638a"},"text":"section 1638a of this title","children":[],"tail":". The substitution in subsec. (a) was made for “retailer” the first time appearing to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"ideedf709c-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"ideedf709d-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 2008 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment of this section and repeal of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234","children":[],"tail":" by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":" effective "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-05-22"},"text":"May 22, 2008","children":[],"tail":", the date of enactment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/234"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–234","children":[],"tail":", see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/246/s4"},"text":"section 4 of Pub. L. 110–246","children":[],"tail":", set out as an Effective Date note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t7/s8701"},"text":"section 8701 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
